#' where \eqn{Y_{B} = Y - \Gamma X} and \eqn{A = \alpha (\alpha^{\prime} \alpha)^{-\frac{1}{2}}}.
#' 
#' The final draws of \eqn{\alpha} and \eqn{\beta} are calculated using
#' \eqn{\beta = B (B^{\prime} B)^{-\frac{1}{2}}} and
